  <brief_title>The Impact of Free Fatty Acid Reduction on Vascular Function in the Metabolic Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Impact of Free Fatty Acid Reduction on Vascular Function in the Metabolic Syndrome</official_title>
